- Files not in the authorized surface (`schedule/__init__.py`, `test_schedule.py`) are off-limits.
- Do not modify, weaken, or remove any existing test.
- Run the full test suite before declaring done: `/opt/homebrew/bin/python3 -m pytest test_schedule.py -q` — must exit 0.

Report your verdict in your final reply text: `PASS` on success; `BLOCKED` if the finding cannot be fixed within the authorized surface.
